quran[3{c,v,t}:
4,24,aur shohar wali aurtain bhi ( tum par haraam hain ) magar woh jo ( aseer ho kar londion ke tor par ) tumahray qabzay mein ajayeen ( yeh hukum ) khuda ne tum ko likh diya hai aur un ( muharmat ) ke siwa aur aurtain tum ko halal hain is terhan se ke maal kharch kar ke un se nikah karlo bashart e kay ( nikah se ) maqsood Iffat qaim rakhna ho nah shehwat rani to jin aurton se tum faida haasil karo un ka mohar jo muqarrarkiya ho ada kardo aur agar muqarrar karne ke baad aapas ki razamandi se mohar mein kami Beshi karlo to tum par kuch gunah nahi be shak khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
4,25,aur jo shakhs tum mein se momin azad aurton ( yani بیبیوں ) se nikah karne ka Maqdoor nah rakhay to momin londion mein hi jo tumahray qabzay mein aagai hon ( nikah karle ) aur khuda tumahray imaan ko achi terhan jaanta hai tum aapas mein aik dosray ke hum jins ho to un londion ke sath un ke malikon se ijazat haasil karkay nikah kar lau aur dastoor ke mutabiq un ka mohar bhi ada kardo bashart e kay Afifa hon nah aisi ke khullam khula badkaari karen aur nah darparda dosti karna chahain phir agar nikah mein aakar badkaari ka irtikaab kar bathain to jo saza azad aurton ( yani bibiyon ) ke liye hai is ki aadhi un ko ( di jaye ) yeh ( londi ke sath nikah karne ki ) ijazat is shakhs ko hai jisay gunah kar bethnay ka andesha ho aur agar sabr karo to yeh tumahray liye bohat acha hai aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
4,26,khuda chahta hai ke ( apni ayatain ) tum se khol khol kar bayan farmaiye aur tum ko aglay logon ke tareeqay betaye aur tum par meharbani kere aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
